Melatonin is a remarkable hormone that plays a crucial role in regulating sleep-wake cycles and supporting healthy sleep patterns. Produced naturally by the body's pineal gland, melatonin helps promote feelings of relaxation and drowsiness, making it easier to fall asleep and stay asleep throughout the night. Additionally, melatonin is a powerful antioxidant that may have potential benefits for immune function, mental health, and even aging. Melatonin supplements are widely available and can be a safe and effective way to support healthy sleep patterns, particularly for those who struggle with insomnia or jet lag. Overall, melatonin is an important hormone that can have a profound impact on overall health and well-being, making it a valuable addition to any healthy lifestyle.

review_title: Most effective we‚Äôve used without side effects
review_text: One serve is 2 gummies 3mg. We give half a serve to our kids who have trouble winding down to sleep. It definitely relaxes them and sends them to sleep. As an adult we have  full serve, and it definitely helps us go to sleep. I‚Äôm an insomniac by default so this really helps me relax, get sleepy, fall asleep and stay asleep. Why I like this brand is because other melatonin has made me groggy in the morning, like having a hangover, but the other thing is other brands send me deep asleep, then jolt me awake at 2am - 3am and I cannot at all go back to sleep. This kills me. I find this brand is gentle but effective. I sleep through and wake up normalish. Definitely my number one choice for melatonin.
